<div class="tags">Tags: <a href="newstag.cgi/linux" title="News items tagged with linux" rel="tag">linux</a>, <a href="newstag.cgi/nederlands" title="News items tagged with nederlands" rel="tag">nederlands</a>, <a href="newstag.cgi/pcgg" title="News items tagged with pcgg" rel="tag">pcgg</a></div>
