<div class="generalitem newsitem"><strong>2008-09-13</strong> (<a href="newsitem.cgi/1221333217" title="Permanent link" rel="bookmark">#</a>) <span class="age">4 years ago</span>
<blockquote>Using the <a href="http://www.voip-info.org/wiki-Asterisk+manager+API">Asterisk manager API</a> it is quite simple to query Asterisk for its status. Using
